---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Brochure Especialización Data Analyst | Data Academy" description="Syllabus oficial e información de la Especialización en Data Analyst (Avanzada). Descarga en formato A4 PDF.">

  <!-- Print Controller -->
  <div class="no-print brochure-bar-wrapper">
    <div class="container bar-container">
      <a href="/ruta-analista?tab=advanced" class="btn btn-outline-light"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Volver a la Ruta</a>
      <div class="bar-actions">
        <button onclick="window.print()" class="btn btn-secondary pulse-btn"><i class="fas fa-file-pdf"></i> Imprimir / Guardar A4 PDF</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- A4 Document Wrapper -->
  <main class="a4-document-container">
    <article class="a4-sheet">
      
      <!-- Minimal Header -->
      <header class="document-header">
        <div class="header-top">
          <div class="brand-logo">
            <span class="logo-bold">DATA</span><span class="logo-light">ACADEMY</span>
          </div>
          <span class="doc-code">REF: DA-SR-2026</span>
        </div>
        <div class="header-main">
          <h1>Especialización en Data Analyst (Senior)</h1>
          <p class="subtitle">Estructura Curricular Oficial · Certificación Profesional A4</p>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- Key Pillars Section (Highlighted Advantages, Projects, Live Classes) -->
      <section class="document-section split-pillars-grid">
        <div class="pillar-card">
          <h4><i class="fas fa-star"></i> Ventajas del Programa</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Temario adaptado a ingeniería de datos en la nube.</li>
            <li>Acceso de por vida a repositorios y clases complementarias.</li>
            <li>Bono de CV de Ingeniero de Datos y bibliografía técnica.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar-card">
          <h4><i class="fas fa-project-diagram"></i> Proyectos de Portafolio</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Construcción de un pipeline completo serverless (Databricks + GCP/Azure).</li>
            <li>Portafolio profesional en GitHub listo para procesos de selección.</li>
            <li>Feedback grupal e individual del código y arquitectura de datos.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar-card">
          <h4><i class="fas fa-video"></i> Clases en Vivo</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Videollamadas periódicas semanales para resolución de arquitecturas.</li>
            <li>Mentorías directas para resolver dudas de sintaxis SQL y PySpark.</li>
            <li>Contacto fluido directo con ingenieros de datos en activo.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Modules List (Minimalist Clean Table / List) -->
      <section class="document-section">
        <h3>Contenido Académico y Módulos</h3>
        <div class="syllabus-list">
          
          <div class="syllabus-row">
            <div class="row-num">01</div>
            <div class="row-content">
              <h4>SQL Server Avanzado</h4>
              <p>Funciones de Ventana (ROW_NUMBER, LEAD, LAG), programación lógica T-SQL (Stored Procedures y Triggers) y tuning de planes de ejecución.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="syllabus-row">
            <div class="row-num">02</div>
            <div class="row-content">
              <h4>Python Profesional & Git</h4>
              <p>Lógica POO aplicada, gestión de logs y excepciones en pipelines de ingesta, y control de versiones con Git, ramas y GitHub Corporativo.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="syllabus-row">
            <div class="row-num">03</div>
            <div class="row-content">
              <h4>Cloud Analytics (BigQuery / Azure Synapse)</h4>
              <p>Ingesta serverless a Buckets, modelado de almacenes de datos analíticos (columnar) y calendarización automática de consultas programadas.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="syllabus-row">
            <div class="row-num">04</div>
            <div class="row-content">
              <h4>Big Data & Spark (Databricks)</h4>
              <p>Procesamiento masivo distribuido con Spark en DataFrames, e implementación de arquitecturas de Medallón (ETL Bronze, Silver, Gold).</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="syllabus-row highlight-row">
            <div class="row-num">05</div>
            <div class="row-content">
              <h4>Proyecto Cloud & Workshop de Automatización (n8n)</h4>
              <p>Desarrollo y automatización del flujo de datos serverless integrando n8n para envío de alertas y reportes a WhatsApp o Slack ante eventos del negocio.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Minimal Registration Footer (Pricing Removed) -->
      <footer class="document-footer" style="justify-content: center; text-align: center; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
        <div class="footer-right no-print" style="align-items: center;">
          <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send/?phone=51927534737&text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20separar%20mi%20vacante%20para%20la%20Especializacion%20Senior%20con%20precio%20preventa" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary btn-whatsapp">Inscribirse por WhatsApp <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i></a>
          <span class="cta-link-doc" style="margin-top: 6px;">Temarios y Promociones: <a href="https://bit.ly/curso_sql_powerbi" target="_blank">https://bit.ly/curso_sql_powerbi</a></span>
        </div>
        <div class="print-only footer-print-note" style="text-align: center; border-top: none; padding-top: 0; margin-top: 0;">
          <p><strong>Matrículas e Inscripciones Académicas:</strong> Contáctanos directamente a nuestro chat oficial: <strong>https://bit.ly/curso_sql_powerbi</strong></p>
        </div>
      </footer>

    </article>
  </main>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Menu header bar */
  .brochure-bar-wrapper {
    background-color: var(--primary-dark);
    padding: 12px 0;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 1000;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .bar-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .btn-outline-light {
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    color: white !important;
    background: transparent;
  }

  .btn-outline-light:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-color: white;
  }

  /* A4 Layout Canvas */
  .a4-document-container {
    background-color: #f8fafc;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  /* Minimal A4 Sheet (DMC style) */
  .a4-sheet {
    background-color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    width: 210mm;
    min-height: 297mm;
    padding: 18mm;
    color: #0f172a;
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  /* Header styles */
  .document-header {
    border-bottom: 2px solid #0f172a;
    padding-bottom: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .header-top {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .brand-logo {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: #0f172a;
  }

  .logo-bold {
    color: #0f172a;
  }

  .logo-light {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .doc-code {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #64748b;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .header-main h1 {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin: 0 0 2px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #64748b;
    margin: 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  /* Key Pillars Section */
  .split-pillars-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .pillar-card {
    background-color: #f8fafc;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 14px;
  }

  .pillar-card h4 {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .pillar-card h4 i {
    color: var(--accent-color);
  }

  .pillar-card ul {
    padding-left: 14px !important;
    margin: 0;
    list-style-type: disc !important;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .pillar-card li {
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }

  /* Section headers */
  .document-section h3 {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: #0f172a;
    border-left: 3px solid #0f172a;
    padding-left: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  /* Syllabus rows */
  .syllabus-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .syllabus-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .syllabus-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .syllabus-row.highlight-row {
    background-color: rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.02);
    padding: 8px 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px dashed rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.25);
  }

  .row-num {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #64748b;
    background-color: #f1f5f9;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .row-content h4 {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin: 0 0 2px;
  }

  .row-content p {
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Document footer layout */
  .document-footer {
    margin-top: auto;
    border-top: 2px solid #0f172a;
    padding-top: 16px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .footer-left {
    flex: 1.4;
  }

  .footer-left h4 {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
  }

  /* Price options box */
  .price-box-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    background-color: #f8fafc;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .price-option-box {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .border-left-divider {
    border-left: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
    padding-left: 16px;
  }

  .price-opt-title {
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #64748b;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .price-val {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .price-old {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #94a3b8;
    text-decoration: line-through;
  }

  .price-note {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: #64748b;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  .reserve-note-text {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #475569;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .footer-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .btn-whatsapp {
    background-color: #25d366;
    color: white !important;
    border: none;
    padding: 9px 18px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.15);
  }

  .btn-whatsapp:hover {
    background-color: #20b858 !important;
  }

  .cta-link-doc {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    color: #64748b;
  }

  .cta-link-doc a {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .print-only {
    display: none;
  }

  /* ==========================================================================
     PRINT INTERFACE STYLES (A4 Tipo DMC)
     ========================================================================== */
  @media print {
    @page {
      size: A4;
      margin: 15mm 20mm;
    }

    .no-print {
      display: none !important;
    }

    body {
      background-color: white !important;
      color: black !important;
    }

    .a4-document-container {
      background: none !important;
      padding: 0 !important;
      min-height: auto !important;
    }

    .a4-sheet {
      box-shadow: none !important;
      padding: 0 !important;
      width: 100% !important;
      min-height: auto !important;
      border: none !important;
    }

    .pillar-card {
      border: 1px solid #cbd5e1 !important;
      background-color: #f8fafc !important;
    }

    .price-box-wrapper {
      border: 1px solid #cbd5e1 !important;
      background-color: #f8fafc !important;
    }

    .syllabus-row.highlight-row {
      background-color: #f8fafc !important;
      border: 1px solid #cbd5e1 !important;
    }

    .print-only {
      display: block !important;
    }

    .footer-print-note {
      font-size: 7.5pt;
      color: #475569;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      padding-top: 6px;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .document-footer {
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }
  }

  /* Responsive styling */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .a4-document-container {
      padding: 10px;
    }

    .a4-sheet {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 20px 14px;
    }

    .split-pillars-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .price-box-wrapper {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .border-left-divider {
      border-left: none;
      border-top: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
      padding-left: 0;
      padding-top: 12px;
    }

    .document-footer {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .footer-right {
      align-items: flex-start;
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
